x4freetext: Detector efficiency determined relative to the
average number of prompt neutrons per spontaneous
fission of Cf-252, taken as 3.732 and Maxwellian
Background, dead time, efficiency, multiple events,
fission events with a multiplicity of 2 neutrons.
data from NSE,74,29,1980 but corrected for the change
in detection efficiency resulting from the difference
between the energy spectra of (n,2n) and fission
M.M. Upper -> lower case correction. Dates
were corrected for 4-digits year. REL-REFs were added.
New ref. R,CEA-R-6447 was added. Subent 004 was added.
